    "description": "In this prologue to the game you fill the shoes of a fresh recruit of the Mercenaries. Get your footing in the land of Wyvia and begin to unravel the mystery of the where the Wyverns have gone. Your mission is simple, find the wyverns, uncover the source of the invasion, and discover your role in saving Wyvia.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prologue Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 open world areas<br></li><li>11 locations<br></li><li>4 classes<br></li><li>2 bosses<br></li><li>12 enemies<br></li><li>21 accessories</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/349398b7b9f36e5ebf45e9f36b7c268f.avif?t=1726259950\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/641ceb807a592f89e9900ce89c87dbc7.poster.avif?t=1726259950\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/641ceb807a592f89e9900ce89c87dbc7.webm?t=1726259950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/641ceb807a592f89e9900ce89c87dbc7.mp4?t=1726259950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wyvia features fun and simple combat that feels good to utilize! Whack Goopies with a huge axe or fire away with screen clearing abilities!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/05a8a6bcf970b568f9fe5a1842ea3684.avif?t=1726259950\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.poster.avif?t=1726259950\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.webm?t=1726259950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.mp4?t=1726259950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mix and match skills between 4 (11 in the full game) distinct classes, allocate points into stats and skills, and create a character that's really your own!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/1a1c0a14d019c458c13d731c39f5556e.avif?t=1726259950\" width=606 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.poster.avif?t=1726259950\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.webm?t=1726259950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.mp4?t=1726259950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a variety of locations from plains, deep caves, spooky forests, and frozen wastes as you struggle against the invasion of monsters in your world and find the source of their intrusion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380780/extras/84493b8eead9e4b41f054cf014880396.avif?t=1726259950\" width=608 height=107 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380